== 效能提升 ==
與DDR3 SDRAM相比，DDR4 SDRAM擁有更高的[[時脈|時脈速率]]以及[[資料傳輸速率|資料傳輸速率]]，初期支援2133至4266MT/s的資料傳輸率，而對於DDR3，JEDEC制定的標準也僅從800至1600MT/s，後期才擴展至2133MT/s，非標準的也只有規格強大但產量較少的2400MT/s。<ref name="xbit">{{citation |url=http://www.xbitlabs.com/news/memory/display/20100816124343_Next_Generation_DDR4_Memory_to_Reach_4_266GHz_Report.html |title=Next-Generation DDR4 Memory to Reach 4.266 GHz |first=Anton |last=Shilov |publisher=Xbitlabs.com |date=2010-08-16 |accessdate=2011-01-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101219085440/http://www.xbitlabs.com/news/memory/display/20100816124343_Next_Generation_DDR4_Memory_to_Reach_4_266GHz_Report.html |archivedate=2010-12-19 }}</ref><ref name="PC Watch"/><ref>{{cite web|title=为发烧而生 金士顿DDR3 2400 8G内存评测|url=http://diy.pconline.com.cn/324/3247313_all.html|accessdate=2014-05-01|archive-date=2014-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502013310/http://diy.pconline.com.cn/324/3247313_all.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>而且，在效能提升的前提下，還比DDR3 SDRAM擁有更好的功耗表現，得益於更高的記憶體顆粒製程以及DDR4-{只}-有1.05V至1.2V的供電[[電壓|電壓]]（DDR3的為1.2V至1.65V），最大[[電流|電流]]值僅和DDR3相當。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.tweaktown.com/news/24799/samsung_announces_16gb_ddr4_dimm_to_be_released_in_2014/index.html |title=Samsung announces 16GB DDR4 DIMM to be released in 2014 :: TweakTown USA Edition |accessdate=2014-05-01 |archive-date=2014-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140128064743/http://www.tweaktown.com/news/24799/samsung_announces_16gb_ddr4_dimm_to_be_released_in_2014/index.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>對於伺服器市場，還提供Banks切換特性，<ref name="PC Watch">{{cite web|last=後藤 弘茂 ("Gotou Shigehiro")|title=メモリ4Gbps時代へと向かう次世代メモリDDR4 ("Towards Next-Generation 4Gbps DDR4 Memory")|url=http://pc.watch.impress.co.jp/docs/column/kaigai/20100816_387444.html|work=2010-08-16|publisher=PC Watch (Japan)|accessdate=2011-04-25|archive-date=2011-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110906084053/http://pc.watch.impress.co.jp/docs/column/kaigai/20100816_387444.html|dead-url=yes}} ([http://translate.google.com/translate?js=y&prev=_t&hl=en&ie=UTF-8&layout=1&eotf=1&u=http%3A%2F%2Fpc.watch.impress.co.jp%2Fdocs%2Fcolumn%2Fkaigai%2F20100816_387444.html&sl=ja&tl=en English translation])</ref>但也就這樣使得伺服器用DDR4記憶體與桌面版本的DDR4記憶體從物理層面上就無法互用。

== 技術細節 ==
